    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ASP_Daily_Bat 是执行器控制器，ASP_Daily_R 对应 PLC 逻辑层。另外还有个 MPOML_Download_Bat，属于遥测数据流，但目前是独立节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ASP_Daily_Bat",
        "ASP_Daily_R",
        "MPOML_Download_Bat",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，已添加三个类节点并标注了角色。现在来看 bc_fwx 这条线，它应该是另一个数据管道入口？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "bc_fwx",
        "ASP_Daily_Bat",
